
### Crear nuevo Scraper (ECA Propiedades)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/scrapers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "UnoPropiedades",
  "url": "https://www.unoinmuebles.com.ar/alquileres",
  "selector": "#main-properties-container",
  "mappings": {
    "title": ".prop-footer > div > p",
    "location": ".font-size: 12px > p",
    "price": "h5.price",
    "imgUrl": ".attachment-property-thumb-image.size-property-thumb-image.wp-post-image",
    "url": "a.more-details",
    "company": "Zuchelli"
  }
}

### LG Inmobiliaria (con paginaciÃ³n)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/scrapers
Content-Type: application/json

{
